Ugh! WoW I seriously cant believe that today was tha day! I didnt actually think it would come to this! back in september I was wishing for this day to come n now that it has I seriously wish we could go back to tha beginning! everything was great! but i kno that i have to move on n forget about it and look at tha bright side of it! I cant believe that my 8th graders are actually leaving and arent gonna be round next year! Im seriously gonna miss you guys like whoa! We all gotta hang out this summer! but yeah today I woke up n got ready then i was reading journals n i started crying....ugh idk why? i just didnt wanna have to go through thsi today! Then i get on tha bus n sit with ashley like every other day n she was talking bout how this was gonna be our last bus ride together n then we were just talking bout other stuff n all tha good times weve had n my eyes got all teary! theres seriously going to be like nobody on my bus next year without them! ugh its okay tho it will all werk out! so then we walked into school n people started crying! i felt so bad! when other people cry it makes me wanna cry! went to 1st hour n got my yearbook n then it was just like a free for all until 5th hour! i got alotta signatures! then during gym ashley n julie came to see me:-) i was very excited! so they both signed my yearbook n then left...:-/ idk im gonna miss them so much! ahh but yeah then we went to drama n me n ellie took pics with nate n brandi n shyt! then on ellies digital camera theres like a recording thing so me n nate did our lil "goodbye" ugh it was so sad! then while walking back i almost started crying again but i held myself back until i saw all tha other 8th graders coming out of there pod balling! marina n kaitlynn signed my yearbook!:-) n then megan came up to me n gave me a realli big hug n she was crying! i felt terrible! i dont want her to leave! ugh but i got on tha bus n started crying n wat not then walked home with kasey for tha last time but we did have alotta laughs! it was fun! so now im just sitting here thinking bout how fricken fast tha year went by! i cant believe it! Thanx to everyone who made it a success im realli gonna miss u!

to my 8th graders....i will always remember our laughs n good times! thanx for everything! im gonna miss u guys so much! never ever change! seriouly only 2 more years! YaY! BfFfFfFfFfFfFfFfFfFfF*etc*

nNn to all tha 7th graders.....i love you guys so much n i wanna say thank u for helping me through evrything this year! hopefully next year is just as good! you realli do mean alot to me n i kno were all gonna be hanging out this summer!8-)


summer 2004.....hell yeah babi!
